{% extends "_base.j2" %}

{% block physics_section %}
PHYSICS
Integer-cell movement. One action = one step.
- LEFT/RIGHT: move 1 cell horizontally.
- JUMP: rise 3 cells (1 per step), plateau 1 step, fall 3 cells (1 per step).
  Total jump arc: 7 steps, peak height 3 cells above launch point.
- JUMP_RIGHT: same arc, but also moves 1 cell right each step.
- Gravity: when in air and not jumping, fall 1 cell per step.
- No double-jump.
- Death: touching P (pit), S (saw blade), m or M (enemy) kills you instantly.

PARTIAL OBSERVABILITY
You see a 20-wide x 12-tall window centered on your position. The level extends
beyond the visible area. Move RIGHT to scroll the view and discover what lies ahead.

STRATEGY
The coin is always at the far right end of the level. Keep moving right, jump
over pits and enemies. Platforms (#) can be used to navigate above ground-level
hazards.
{% endblock %}
